import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Open Start menu
    pyautogui.hotkey('win')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Type calculator
    pyautogui.typewrite('calculator', interval=0.05)
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Press Enter to launch
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED:", str(e))
